\id HOS
\h Ḥuciɛa 
\toc1 Ḥuciɛa 
\toc2 Ḥuciɛa 
\toc3 Ḥuc. 
\mt1 Ḥuciɛa  
\c 1
\m
\v 1 Awař n SIDI i dd-yusin ɣar Ḥuciɛa, mmis n Biri, deg wussan n Ɛuzziya, Yutam, Aḥaz d Ḥizqiya, ijeǧiden n Yahuda, u deg wussan n Yarubɛam, mmis n Yuwac, ajeǧid n Israil. \f ◼ \fr 1:1 \ft \+fk Ḥuciɛa\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘asenjem’ niɣ ‘afřaḥ’. \fk Biri\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘anu inu’. \fk Ḥizqiya\ft  - isem nnes ikemmřen ‘Yaḥizqiya’.\f*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ḥuciɛa yejj-dd třata n iḥenjiren ɣar Xumar  
\m
\v 2 Abeddu n wawař n SIDI s Huciɛa. SIDI inna i Huciɛa: “Ruḥ, awi ict n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř uřa d tarwa n farq-ccɣeř, maɣar s farq-ccɣeř \add nnes\add* tezna temmurt \add teffeɣ\add* zeg awarni i SIDI.”  
\v 3 Uca yuyur netta, yiwi Jumar, yeǧis n Diblayim, u nettat teksi s ddeyset, turuw as-dd ijj n mmis. \f ◼ \fr 1:3 \ft \+fk Diblayim\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘tnayen n tɣayiṭat n tazart’.\f*  
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* inna as SIDI: “Řaɣa as s yisem n ‘Yazraɛil’, maɣar cwayt n řweqt \add waha\add* u \add xenni\add* Necc ad xeǧṣeɣ idammen n Yazraɛil x taddart n Yahu u Necc ad qḍiɣ x tgelda n taddart n Israil. \f ◼ \fr 1:4 \ft \+fk Yazraɛil\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘Arebbi ad izeǧeɛ’ niɣ ‘Arebbi ad izarɛ’ niɣ ‘aɣiř n Arebbi’.\f*  
\v 5 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad yiři, aqa Necc ad arẓeɣ řqews n Israil di řewḍa n teɣzurt n Yazraɛil.” \f ◼ \fr 1:5 \ft \+fk řqews n Israil\ft  - tuɣa řgens n Israil ittwassen aqa ɣarsen aṭṭas n imejjaben n řqews.\f*   
\m
\v 6 Uca teksi nettat ɛawed s ddeyset, turuw-dd yeǧis uca inna as \add SIDI\add*: “Řaɣa as s yisem n Lu-Ruḥama, maɣar war arreḥḥmeɣ ɛad x taddart n Israil, war ttɣimiɣ semmḥeɣ asen. \f ◼ \fr 1:6 \ft \+fk Lu-Ruḥama\ft  - isem wanita-a ixs ad yini ‘war arreḥmeɣ’.\f*  
\v 7 \add Maca\add* ad arreḥmeɣ x taddart n Yahuda u Necc ad ten ssnejmeɣ s \add ufus n\add* SIDI, AREBBI nsen! Necc war ten ssenjmeɣ s řqews niɣ s ssif niɣ s iysan uřa s imnayen.” \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt Zak. 4:6\x*   
\m
\v 8 \add Ařami\add* tekkes uṭṭuḍ i Lu-Ruḥama, teksi \add ɛawed\add* s ddeyset uca turuw-dd ijj n mmis.  
\v 9 Uca inna \add SIDI\add*: “Řaɣa as s yisem n Lu-Ɛammi, maɣar kenniw war teǧim ɛad d řgens inu u Necc war ǧiɣ \add ɛad da\add* i kenniw.” \f ◼ \fr 1:9 \ft \+fk Lu-Ɛammi\ft  - isem wanita-a ixs ad yini ‘war iǧi řgens inu’.\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Amenḍar n Israil d weɛdař nnes  
\m
\v 1 “Ad yiři řqedd n ayt n Israil am yejdi n řebḥar i war izemmar ad ittwaɛbar u war izemmar ad ittwaḥseb, uca ad tafed mani d asen nnan: ‘Kenniw war teǧim d řgens inu!’, ad asen ittwanna: ‘Kenniw d iḥenjiren n Arebbi iddaren!’ \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt Amz. 32:11; Rum. 9:25, 26\x*  
\v 2 Ayt n Yahuda d ayt n Israil ad ttwassmunen, ad ggen ijj n umɣar i yixef nsen u ad geɛɛden zi \add marra\add* temmurt, maɣar ass n Yazraɛil ad yiři d ijj n wass d ameqqran. \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt Ica. 11:13; Irm. 3:18; Ḥiz. 37:16, 22; Afa. 2:14, 15, 16\x*  
\v 3 Inim i wawmaten nwem: ‘Ɛemmi!’ u i suyᵉtmatwem ‘Ruḥama!’   
\b  
\m
\v 4 “Dɛam ak-d yemmatwem, dɛam, maɣar nettat war teǧi d tamɣart inu u Necc war ǧiɣ d aryaz nnes. Ejj i-tt ad tekkes farq-ccɣeř nnes zeg uɣembub nnes uřa d zzina zi jar ibbac nnes.  
\v 5 Niɣ aqa ad as kkseɣ arruḍ ad tt jjeɣ d taɛaryant¸ ad tt ssarseɣ \add diha\add* am deg wass amezwaru i di dd-texřeq, \add wah,\add* ad tt arreɣ d ict n řexřa, ad tt arreɣ am yict n temmurt yuẓɣen uca ad tt jjeɣ ad temmet s ufadi.  
\v 6 Necc war arreḥmeɣ x iḥenjiren nnes, maɣar nitni d iḥenjiren \add i dd-ixeřqen\add* zi farq-ccɣeř.  
\v 7 Maɣar yemmatsen aqa tefsed ixef nnes, \add wah,\add* tenni tuɣa s ddeyset zzaysen, tegga řefḍiḥet, maɣar teqqar: ‘Ad ḍfareɣ inni d ayi iɛeccqen, inni d ayi itticen aɣrum inu d waman inu d taḍuft inu d tiffest inu d zzect inu d tsessit inu.’  
\v 8 S uya, aqa ad bellɛeɣ abrid nnem s cbarq ak-d isennanen u ad ssbeddeɣ aɣbar nnes, ḥima war tᵉttif \add ɛad\add* imesraq nnes.  
\v 9 Nettat ad teḍfar inni tt iɛecqen, maca war xasen tḥarret. Nettat ad xasen tarzu, \add maca\add* war ten tᵉttif. Xenni ad tini: ‘Necc ad ɛeqbeɣ, ad dewřeɣ ɣar weryaz inu amezwaru, maɣar deg wussan nni tuɣa ayi mliḥ x řexxu.’  
\v 10 Nettat war teɛqiř, aqa d Necc i tuɣa d as iwcin imendi d binu n jdid d zzect, u aqa d Necc i tuɣa d as iwcin nnuqart s waṭṭas, uca ureɣ \add i d asen wciɣ\add* aqa ggin t ɣar Baɛl.  
\v 11 S uya i ɣa ɛeqbeɣ, ad kkseɣ imendi inu di řweqt n ṣṣabet uřa d binu inu n jdid di řweqt nnes ittwaggen u taḍuft inu d tiffest inu i zi teddař tuɛɛaryent nnes ad \add tent\add* qeřɛeɣ \add zzayes\add*.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* řexxu ad ɛarriɣ x řeḥya nnes zzat i tiṭṭawin n yinni tt ittexsen uca uřa d ijjen war izemmar ad tt ifekk zeg ifassen inu.  
\v 13 Necc ad ssbeddeɣ marra řefraḥet nnes, uraren nnes, ussan nnes n ubeddi n uyur uřa d ussan nnes n ssebt, \add wah,\add* marra ussan nnes ittwaggen.  
\v 14 Ad areddǧeɣ tazayart nnes d \add tcejjart n\add* wartu nnes i zi tenna: ‘Tina d řmunet i d ayi wcin yinni d ayi ittexsen.’ Ad tent arreɣ d ijj n wezɣar u řmař n yeyyar ad zzaysent ccen. \f ◼ \fr 2:14 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:14 \xt Izhd. 80:13; Ica. 5:5\x*  
\v 15 Necc ad tt wteɣ x ussan n ‘Ibaɛlen’, \add ussan\add* i di tiwi-dd asen tiwhibin n řebxur u tegga taxrazt nnes d tseddect nnes, u teḍfar inni tt ittexsen, \add maca\add* nettat tᵉttu ayi!”, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.   
\b  
\m
\v 16 “S uya, xzar, Necc ad tt ɣarreɣ, ad tt nedheɣ ɣar řexřa, u \add din\add* ad ssiwřeɣ ak-d wuř nnes.  
\v 17 Ssenni ad as wceɣ imarjaɛen nnes n uḍiř u ad arreɣ taɣzurt n Axur d tawwart n řayas. Nettat ad dinni tɣennej am \add tɣennej\add* deg wussan n temẓi nnes, am x wass umi dd-teffeɣ zi temmurt n Miṣra.  
\v 18 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* iqqar SIDI, ad ayi třaɣid: ‘Aryaz inu!’, u war d ayi teqqared ɛad: ‘Baɛl inu!’  
\v 19 Ad as kkseɣ ismawen n ‘Ibaɛlen’ zeg uqemmum nnes. War ttfekkaren ɛad deg ismawen nsen.  
\v 20 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad ggeɣ ijj n řɛahd di ṭṭweɛ nsen ak-d řewḥuc n řexřa, ak-d ijḍaḍ n ujenna u ak-d imuddaren nni ittbuɛen x wudem n temmurt. Ad kkseɣ řqews d ssif d umenɣi zi temmurt u ad ten ssarreyḥeɣ di řhudnet. \f ◼ \fr 2:20 \ft \+fk ad ggeɣ\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ad qesseɣ’. \fk ad kkseɣ\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ad arẓeɣ’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:20 \xt Ayub 5:23; Ica. 11:6; Ḥiz. 14:21; 34:25\x*  
\v 21 Necc ad cem xeḍbeɣ i řebda, \add wah,\add* ad cem xeḍbeɣ s tsegda d řheqq, s tmexsiwt icewwaren d arreḥmet.  
\v 22 Necc ad cem xeḍbeɣ s řaman, u cem ad tessned SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 2:22 \xt Irm. 31:33, 34\x*  
\v 23 \bd Deg wass nni\bd*, iqqar SIDI, ad imsar aqa Necc ad sřeɣ ɣar ujenna u ajenna ad iseř ɣar temmurt  
\v 24 u tammurt ad tseř ɣar imendi uřa ɣar binu n jdid d zzect, u ina ad sřen ɣar Yazraɛil.  
\v 25 Necc ad tt zarɛeɣ i Necc di temmurt u Necc ad arreḥmeɣ x Lu-Ruḥama, u ad iniɣ i Lu-Ɛammi: ‘Cem d řgens inu i teǧid!’, u \add řgens\add* ad yini: ‘AREBBI inu!’” \x ◘ \xo 2:25 \xt Ḥuc. 2:1; Rum. 9:26; 1 Bṭ. 2:10\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Ḥuciɛa ad iseɣ ict n temɣart izennan  
\m
\v 1 SIDI inna ayi: “Ruḥ ict n twařa nneɣni, exs tamɣart nni ittwassɛizzen zeg umeddukkeř \add nnes\add*, \add maca\add* tezna, am mammec SIDI ittexs ayt n Israil, \add maca\add* nitni xezzaren ɣar irebbiten nneɣni u ttexsen \add ṣṣedqet\add* n weɣrum s zzbib.” \f ◼ \fr 3:1 \ft \+fk tenni ittwassɛizzen zeg umeddukkeř\ft  - zi jjihet n tterjama aqa din jar yinni ittfessaren Adlis Iqeddsen array ifarzen, maca neccin nḍeffar array i iqqaren belli Arebbi inna i Ḥuciɛa belli ad yawi Jumir ɛawed d tamɣart nnes. Deg ayet i dd-ittasen awarni tanita iban-dd aqa ittxeṣṣa i Ḥuciɛa ad ixeǧeṣ ṣṣadaq ɛawed, maca qell x min tuɣa nnumen yeryazen ad xeǧṣen (řqimet n ṣṣadaq tuɣa tt 50 n řweznat n nnuqart - xzar Aɛwd. 22:29), maca Ḥuciɛa ixeǧeṣ řqimet n 30 n řweznat n nnuqart waha. Aqa balak tuɣa man aya minzi Jumir tuɣa tfessed arrimet nnes.\f*  
\v 2 \add S uyenni\add* sɣiɣ tt i necc s xemmesṭac n \add uqiyyat n\add* nnuqart u s ijj n uḥumir ifeyyḍen n imendi.  
\v 3 Necc nniɣ as: “Cem ad ɣari teqqimed aṭṭas n wussan. War ttegg ca farq-ccɣeř u war ttiři n ijj n weryaz nneɣni, uca uřa d necc ad ggeɣ amenni akidsem.” \x ◘ \xo 3:3 \xt Aɛwd. 21:11\x*  
\v 4 Maɣar ayt n Israil ad qqimen aṭṭas n wussan břa ajeǧid, břa řḥakem, břa taɣarṣt, břa amayḍu \add iqeddsen\add*, břa apalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* d řexyařat n l’aṣnam. \x ◘ \xo 3:4 \xt Ḥuc. 10:3\x*  
\v 5 Awarni as ad dd-dewřen ayt n Israil¸ ad arzun x SIDI, AREBBI nsen u x Dawud, ajeǧid nsen. Deg uneggar n wussan ad dd-asen ttarjijin ɣar SIDI d tcuni nnes. \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Ica. 2:2; Irm. 30:9; Ḥiz. 34:23; 37:22; Mixa 4:1\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Awař n SIDI ḍidd i ikehhanen d řgens  
\m
\v 1 “Sřem i wawař n SIDI, ayt n Israil, maɣar SIDI iksi tanfuč ḍidd i imezdaɣ n temmurt, minzi war din yeǧi řaman niɣ tamexsiwt icewwaren uřa d tussna n AREBBI di temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 4:1 \xt Mixa 6:2\x*  
\v 2 Tikkʷura d ixarriqen d umenɣi d tucceffra d zzina! Aqa aten dduqqzen, asizzeř n idammen awarni i usizzeř n idammen.  
\v 3 X uya tceṭṭen tammurt u kuř ijjen i dayes izeddɣen ittaẓeɣ: řewḥuc n yeyyar d yijḍaḍ n ujenna, \add wah,\add* uřa d iseřman di řebḥar ttwakksen.  
\v 4 Maca uct x weryaz nni i d ɣa iksin tanfuč u uct x weryaz nni i ɣa icetcan. Řgens nnec axmi yinni ittemcubbcen ak-d ukehhan.  
\v 5 S uziř ad tenqarḍed u s ǧiřet ad inqarḍ ɛad anabi akidek, u yemmac ad tt sshellkeɣ.  
\v 6 Řgens inu idweř d aynaw, minzi aqa-t břa tussna. Umi cek tenḍared tussna, nḍareɣ cek maḥend war d ayi tsexxared \add ɛad\add* am ukehhan. \add Umi\add* cek tᵉttud Ccariɛa n AREBBI, uřa d Necc ad ttuɣ iḥenjiren nnec.  
\v 7 Mammec ma ktaren, arnin di ddnub akidi. Ad arreɣ ccan nsen d řefḍiḥet.  
\v 8 Nitni ttᵉtten zi ddnub n řgens inu u s wuř nsen ttarran meẓri i řmuɛṣiyyet nsen.  
\v 9 Am mammec \add i iǧa\add* ukehhan, ammu i ɣa yiři uřa d řgens. Necc ad dayes xeřfeɣ ibriden nnes u timegga nnes ad as tent xeǧṣeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 4:9 \xt Ica. 24:2\x*  
\v 10 Nitni ad ccen, maca war tᵉttjjiwinen ca, nitni ad ssfesden ixef nsen, maca war ttmarenyen, minzi nitni semḥen deg uḥettu n \add tsexxart i\add* SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 4:10 \xt Mixa 6:14\x*  
\v 11 Farq-ccɣeř d binu u binu n jdid aqa kksen uř \add i bnadem\add*.  
\v 12 Řgens inu ittseqsa \add ṣṣanam nnes\add* n ukeccuḍ u taɣɣarct nnes ad as tewc řexbar, minzi buḥbeř n farq-ccɣeř iɣarra i-ten ařami ffɣen s farq-ccɣeř nsen zi sadu \add aḥeṭṭu n\add* AREBBI nsen. \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Ḥuc. 5:4\x*  
\v 13 X tqiccat n idurar ttqeddamen tiɣarṣa u x tewriririn ttawyen tiwhibin n řebxur, sadu řbeǧuḍ d ṣṣefṣaf d tcejjart n yigg, minzi tiři nsen teṣbeḥ. X uya ssefsadent yessitwem ixef nsent u tisřatin nwem ttareẓẓant řemřac s zzina. \x ◘ \xo 4:13 \xt Ica. 1:29; 57:7; Ḥiz. 20:28\x*  
\v 14 Maca Necc war ssiwiḍeɣ řḥukm x yessitwem umi ssfesdent ixef nsent uřa x tesřatin nwem umi ttareẓẓant řemřac s zzina. Aqa nitenti ḥuzent ixef nsent ak-d temɣarin n farq-ccɣeř u ttqeddament tiɣarṣa \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d temɣarin n farq-ccɣeř n zzawect. Ad iwḍa řgens i war ɣar iǧi řeɛqeř.”   
\m
\v 15 “Waxxa cek, Israil, tessefseded ixef nnec, war ttarri uřa d Yahuda d bu-umarwas. War dd-ttisim ɣar Jiljal, war ttgeɛɛadem ɣar Bayt-Awan u war ttjaǧam: ‘\add S tidett am\add* iddar SIDI!’  
\v 16 Minzi Israil dayes taɣennant am yict n tfunast tɛarren. \add Xenni\add* řexxu, ad ten yarwes SIDI am yijj n yezmar ameẓyan deg iyyar iwesɛen aṭṭas.  
\v 17 Ifrayim iqqen ixef nnes ak-d řexyařat n l’aṣnam, ejj i-t, ismeḥ dayes.  
\v 18 Tasessit nsen dayes ssem, tteggen farq-ccɣeř awarni i farq-ccɣeř, u imeḥḍayen nsen ttexsen mɣir řefḍiḥet waha.  
\v 19 Ict n tḥaryaḍt tessjebd i-tt s wafriwen nnes: aqa nitni ad dewřen ttseḍḥan zi tɣarṣi nsen.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 Řḥukm x Israil d ikehhanen nnes  
\m
\v 1 “Sřem aya, \add kenniw\add* ikehhanen, ḥḍam \add kenniw ayt n\add* taddart n Israil u wcem amezzuɣ, kenniw, \add aytbab n\add* taddart n ujeǧid, maɣar tdewřem d ijj n řfex di Miṣfat d ict n tracca yarezmen x \add wedrar n\add* Tabur.  
\v 2 Inni i dd-itteffɣen zeg webrid ssiǧɣen tasraft n wenɣay, maca Necc ad ten ɛaqbeɣ marra.  
\v 3 Necc ssneɣ Ifrayim u Israil war izemmar ad zzayi innuffar. Maɣar řexxu issefsed Ifrayim ixef nnes, Israil issexmej ixef nnes.  
\v 4 Timegga nsen tmennɛent i-ten ad dd-dewřen ɣar AREBBI, maɣar ijj n buḥbeř n farq-ccɣeř aqa-t di řwesṭ nsen uca war ssinen SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 5:4 \xt Ḥuc. 4:12\x*  
\v 5 Aɛeffar n Israil ad xas idɛa s bṭayṭay. Israil d Ifrayim ad nqarḍen zi řmuɛṣiyyet nsen uřa d Yahuda ad kidsen inqarḍ. \x ◘ \xo 5:5 \xt Ḥuc. 7:10\x*  
\v 6 Nitni ad aggʷejen ak-d wuǧi nsen d ifunasen d tfunasin nsen, ḥima ad arzun x SIDI, maca nitni war t ttifen. Netta aqa issnuffar ixef nnes xasen.  
\v 7 Nitni ɣdaren SIDI maɣar nitni jjin-dd tarwa n farq-ccɣeř. Řexxu ad ten yecc uyur amaynu ak-d tseqqař nsen n řwart.”   
\m
\v 8 “Suḍem deg uyicc n icarri di Jibɛa, di řbuq di Rama, ad sɣuyen \add imezdaɣ n\add* Bayt-Awan: ‘Awarni ac, a Binyamin!’  
\v 9 Ifrayim ad idweř d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ deg wass n lɛiqab. Necc barrḥeɣ jar tqebbař n Israil min ittwagg ad imsar.  
\v 10 Řḥukkam n Yahuda tteggen am yinni issmuṭṭuyen iẓra n weymir. Necc ad xasen zeǧɛeɣ aduqqez inu \add n ufugem\add* am waman.”   
\m
\v 11 “Ifrayim ittwaḥṣar, řḥeqq ittwařbez, maɣar iɛjeb as maḥend ad iḍfar ict n tewṣeyyet \add n řbaṭeř\add*.  
\v 12 Necc am tcinda i Ifrayim u am ureṣṣuḍ i taddart n Yahuda.  
\v 13 \add Umi\add* iẓra Ifrayim řehřac nnes u Yahuda tareḥsit nnes, yuyur Ifrayim ɣar Accur, issekk \add ijj n ureqqas\add* ɣar ujeǧid Yarib. \add Maca\add* wanita war izemmar ad kenniw issgenfa u war xawem ikessi tareḥsit nwem. \f ◼ \fr 5:13 \ft \+fk Yarib\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘amcubbec’.\f*  
\v 14 Maɣar Necc ad iřiɣ i Ifrayim am weyrad izehharen u am weyrad ameẓyan i taddart n Yahuda. Necc, \add wah\add* Necc, ad mezzqeɣ u \add xenni\add* ad uyureɣ, ad t awyeɣ uca war din wi ɣa ifekken.  
\v 15 Necc ad ffɣeɣ u \add xenni\add* ad ɛeqbeɣ ɣar wemcan inu, ař ɣa neɛmen u ad arzun udem inu. Di řeḥṣaret nsen ad xafi arzun zic ɣar ṣṣbeḥ.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\s1 Ařaɣi n Ḥuciɛa i ttubet  
\m
\v 1 “Asem-dd, ad dd-nedweř ɣar SIDI, maɣar Netta iqezzar, \add maca\add* ad aneɣ issgenfa, Netta iwta, \add maca\add* ad aneɣ icfen.  
\v 2 Awarni tnayen n wussan ad aneɣ yarr ɣar tudart, deg wass wiss třata ad aneɣ issnekkar u neccin ad neddar zzat i wudem nnes.  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* ad nessen, ad neḍfar maḥend ad nessen SIDI. Aḍhar nnes imten am tuffut n řefjar. Ad ɣarneɣ dd-yas am wenẓar, am wenẓar n arbiɛ nni issarḍaben tammurt.” \f ◼ \fr 6:3 \ft \+fk arbiɛ\ft  - niɣ ‘tafsut’\f*  \x ◘ \xo 6:3 \xt Izhd. 19:5, 6\x*   
\m
\v 4 “Min akidek ɣa ggeɣ, \add a\add* Ifrayim, min akidek ɣa ggeɣ, \add a\add* Yahuda. Tamexsiwt nwem icewwaren tᵉttegg am useynu ɣar teffut u am nnda igeɛɛden uca \add xenni\add* iqeṭṭa.  
\v 5 X uya Necc qesseɣ \add ten\add* s \add tmijja n\add* inabiyyen \add am\add* s ijj n uyeřzim. Necc nɣiɣ ten s wawařen n uqemmum inu. Řeḥkamat xak \add amecnaw\add* tfawt innufsřen.  
\v 6 Minzi ttexseɣ tamexsiwt icewwaren, war iǧi taɣarṣt, u tussna n SIDI \add ttexseɣ tt\add* x tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ.” \x ◘ \xo 6:6 \xt Mt. 9:13; 12:7\x*   
\m
\v 7 “Nitni ɛeddan x Řɛahd am Adam. Dinni i d ayi ɣdaren. \x ◘ \xo 6:7 \xt Ḥuc. 8:1\x*  
\v 8 Jilɛad d ict n tendint n yinni itteggen řmuɛṣiyyet, teccur s idammen.  
\v 9 Am yijj n bandiyya n ixewwanen i ittrajan ca n yijjen, ammu \add i teǧa\add* terfiqt n ikehhanen. Nitni neqqen deg webrid i dd ittawyen ɣar Cakim, maɣar nitni tteggen řefḍayeḥ \add waha\add*.  
\v 10 Necc ttwařiɣ tamesřact tessnexřaɛ di taddart n Israil, xzar, farq-ccɣeř n Ifrayim, Israil tessexmej ixef nnes.”   
\m
\v 11 “\add Waxxa amenni\add*, \add a\add* Yahuda, aqa temmars ict n ṣṣabet i cek, xmi dd ɣa ssɛeqbeɣ imeḥbas n řgens inu.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\s1 Ifrayim war ixs ad itub  
\m
\v 1 “Am ssgenfiɣ Israil, tᵉttwaɛarr řmuɛṣiyyet n Ifrayim d tuɛeffna n Samarya, maɣar nitni tteggen s řɣecc. Aceffar ittadef u ict n bandiyya tᵉttkeccaḍ di barra.  
\v 2 \add Maca\add* war qqaren \add ɛemmarṣ\add* deg wuř nsen, aqa Necc ad xarrṣeɣ di marra řɣar nsen. Xenni řexxu, nnḍent asen tmegga nsen, aqa atent zzat i wudem inu.  
\v 3 Nitni ssfraḥen ajeǧid s řɣar nsen u řḥukkam \add ssfraḥen ten\add* s ixarriqen nsen.  
\v 4 Nitni marra d imzennayen, aqa aten am yijj n ufarran nni ittwasseḥman zeg uxebbaz. Wanita ad issbedd zeg ucemmuḍ awarni řami ggʷin arecti ař ismem \add qaɛ\add*.  
\v 5 Deg wass n ujeǧid nneɣ ssheřcen řḥukkam ixef nsen s řḥaduq n binu. Netta isswiẓẓeḍ afus nnes i yimestehzayen.  
\v 6 Xmi dd-ttqarraben, \add yareqq\add* uř nsen am yijj n ufarran zi tḥraymect nsen. Itteṭṭeṣ uxebbaz nsen ǧiřet tekmeř. Ɣar ṣṣbeḥ yareqq \add ufarran\add* am tmessi itteḥduduqen.  
\v 7 Nitni marra ḥemman am yijj n ufarran u nitni ttᵉtten řquḍat nsen. Marra ijeǧiden nsen ad wḍan, war din uřa d ijj jar asen i dd xafi ɣa iřaɣan.”   
\b  
\m
\v 8 “Ifrayim ijja ixef nnes issur jar řegnus, Ifrayim d ict n tefḍiřt war tᵉttwassneqřeb ca. \x ◘ \xo 7:8 \xt Izhd. 106:35\x*  
\v 9 Ibarraniyyen sarḍen jjehd nnes, war akides ittici. Uřa d acuwwaf nnes ittcab, war akides ittici.  
\v 10 Aɛeffar n Israil ad xas idɛa, \add maɣar\add* nitni war ddikkwiřen ca ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nsen, u war t arzun ca di marra man aya. \x ◘ \xo 7:10 \xt Ḥuc. 5:5\x*  
\v 11 Ifrayim igga am yict n tedbirt aḥafi, war dayes řefhamet. Nitni ttřaɣan x Miṣra, gguren ɣar Accur.  
\v 12 Xmi gguren nitni, ttbezzaɛeɣ Necc tracca inu xasen, ad ten dd-ssehwiɣ am yijḍaḍ n ujenna, ad ten webbxeɣ x řeḥsab n řexbar zi jjhet n tmesmunt nsen.  
\v 13 Uct xasen maɣar nitni arewřen zzayi. Akeḥḥeḍ xasen, maɣar nitni ɛeddan xafi. Necc ggiɣ ad ten fdiɣ, maca nitni nnan xafi ixarriqen.  
\v 14 Nitni war dd-sɣuyen ca ɣari s wuř nsen, xmi ṭṭṣen nitni x řectu nsen ttcetcan. Nitni ttmunan di ṭṭweɛ n imendi d binu n jdid, aqa ttɣennan xafi.  
\v 15 Necc darrbeɣ u ssjehdeɣ iɣaǧen nsen, \add maca\add* nitni ttxarraṣen dayi di řɣar.  
\v 16 Nitni ttɛaqqaben, maca war iǧi ɣar Umɛuǧi x kuřci. Aqa aten am yijj n řqews ixeṭṭan, řḥukkam nsen weṭṭan zi ssif, zi semm ineqqen n yiřes nsen. S uyenni ad xasen ggen tiḍeḥḥac di temmurt n Miṣra.” \x ◘ \xo 7:16 \xt Izhd. 78:57\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\s1 Iqarreb-dd řḥukm x weɛbed n Ifrayim i l’aṣnam  
\m
\v 1 “Ggem icc n icarri \add i usuḍi\add* ɣar uqemmum nnec. Am yijj n ugider \add iṭṭaw netta\add* sennej i Taddart n SIDI, maɣar nitni ɛeddan x Řɛahd inu u ɣewwɣen x Ccariɛa inu. \x ◘ \xo 8:1 \xt Aɛwd. 28:49; Ḥuc. 6:7 \x*  
\v 2 Nitni ad xafi dd-řaɣan: ‘AREBBI inu, neccin, Israil, aqa nessen Cek!’  
\v 3 Israil inḍar min iṣebḥen, řeɛdu ad t iḍfar.   
\m
\v 4 Nitni ggin \add xasen\add* ijeǧiden, \add maca\add* nitni war ǧin ca zzayi, nitni areccḥen řḥukkam, maca Necc war \add tt\add* ssineɣ. Nitni ggin řexyařat n l’aṣnam i yixef nsen, s uyenni ad ittwaqess \add řexyař nni\add*.  
\v 5 Aɛejmi nnec d ijj n nnɛi, \add a\add* Samarya! Aɣḍab inu yareqq qibač nsen. Ař meřmi ɣa qqimen nitni war zemmaren ad ksin tazdugi? \f ◼ \fr 8:5 \ft \+fk Aɛejmi nnec\ft  - aɛejmi-ya war tuɣi ibedd di Samarya, maca di Bitil (xzar Ḥuciɛa 10:5, 15).\f*  
\v 6 Maɣar \add iffeɣ-dd řexyař n ṣṣanam\add* zi Israil, aqa ijj n bu-ṣṣenɛet igga i-t u wanita war iǧi d AREBBI. Wah, \add ad idweř řexyař\add* d iwetwiten, aɛejmi n Samarya.  
\v 7 Maɣar nitni zarrɛen asemmiḍ u mejjaren taḥaryaḍt. War ttifen \add tidrin\add* ɣar iɣedduyen, u zeg imendi ibedden war zzaysen tteggen ssmid, niɣ ad ittwagg, \add maca\add* ad t ṣarḍen ibarraniyyen.”   
\m
\v 8 “Aqa Israil ittwaṣarḍ. \bd Řexxu\bd* dewřen am yict n řqecɛet jar řegnus, war dd-tusi x řxaḍar i ḥed.  
\v 9 Maɣar nitni geɛɛden ɣar Accur. Ijj n weɣyuř n řexřa ittɣima i yixef nnes waha, \add maca inni n\add* Ifrayim ttxeǧaṣen i imḥibban \add nsen\add*.  
\v 10 Waxxa nitni zzenzen ixef nsen i řegnus, maca ggur \bd řexxu\bd* ad ten yarweɣ. Nitni war zemmaren ad ggen mɣir drus waha zi ssibbet n zzeyyar n ujeǧid n řḥukkam.  
\v 11 Maɣar Ifrayim igga iɛalṭaren nnes d aṭṭas, ḥima ad \add zzaysen\add* iddenb. Aqa dewřen d iɛalṭaren n ddenb i netta.  
\v 12 Necc uriɣ as aṭṭas n tmesřayin zi Ccariɛa inu, \add maca\add* nitni ḥesben xasent am ca n řḥajjet d taɣribt.  
\v 13 Zi tɣarṣa n ṣṣdaqi inu, aqa nitni wehhben zzaysent aysum uca ttᵉtten zzayes, \add maca\add* SIDI war zzaysen yareṭṭi. \bd Řexxu\bd* ad ixarreṣ di řmuɛṣiyyet nsen u Netta ad ixeǧeṣ ddnub nsen. Ad dd-dewřen ɣar Miṣra.  
\v 14 Maɣar Israil ittu wenni t iggin, ibna tizawiyyin, uca Yahuda ikettar tineddam ifaryen, \add maca\add* Necc ad ssekkeɣ ict n tmessi di tneddam nnes, ad tecc řeqṣur nnes.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\m
\v 1 “War farreḥ ca ammu, Israil, ařami i ɣa tesřiwřiwed am řegnus. Maɣar tiggʷejed x AREBBI nnec am tessefseded ixef nnec. Tettexsed řmunet n ict n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř di marra inedrar n usarwet n imendi.  
\v 2 Andrar d tsirt n uḍiř war d asen sseccen ca u binu n jdid ad tt ixeyyeb.  
\v 3 Nitni war ttɣiman ca di temmurt n SIDI. Ifrayim ad dd-idweř ɣar Miṣra u nitni ad ccen min ixemjen di Accur.  
\v 4 Nitni war seyyben ca \add tiwhibin n\add* binu i SIDI u tiɣarṣa nsen war xas areṭṭant. Ad asen iřint am weɣrum n yinni iceṭṭnen. Marra inni t iccen, ad dewřen xemjen, maɣar aɣrum nsen \add ad yiři\add* i řeɛmar nsen, war dd-ittis di Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 5 Min ɣa teggem \add xenni\add* deg ijj n wass \add n řɛid\add* ittwaggen, deg wass n Řɛid n SIDI?  
\v 6 Maɣar, xzar, aqa nitni ttaggʷejen zi ssibbet n ureddeǧ. Miṣra ad ten issmun, Muf ad ten tenḍeř. Irezzazen ad meẓẓren di nnuqart nsen, cbarq ak-d isennanen ad iṭṭef amcan n iqiḍan nsen. \f ◼ \fr 9:6 \ft \+fk Muf\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘Mimfis’, tandint taqdimt aṭṭas n Miṣra. Ad tafed isem wanita di Ica. 19:13, Irm. 2:16, 44:1 d Ḥiz. 30:13, 16 d Huciya 9:6.\f*   
\m
\v 7 Aqa ussan n ujarreb usin-dd, aqa ussan n lɛiqab usin-dd. Nitni ad \add tt\add* ssnen, \add inni n\add* Israil. Anabi \add am yijj n\add* abuhaři \add i nitni\add*, aryaz arruḥani \add am yijj n\add* bu-jnun zeg waṭṭas n řmuɛṣiyyet nnec d waṭṭas n řeɛdawet nnec.  
\v 8 Aɛessas n Ifrayim \add ittɛessas\add* ak-d \add uɛawen n\add* AREBBI inu, \add wah, netta,\add* anabi \add ittaf\add* ijj n řfex n unegmar di marra ibriden nnes, řeɛdawet di Taddart n AREBBI nnes. \x ◘ \xo 9:8 \xt Irm. 6:17\x*  
\v 9 \add Maɣar\add* aqa aten ɣarqen ař iři, am deg wussan nni n Jibɛa. Netta ad iɛqeř x řmuɛṣiyyet nsen u ad ixřef ddnub nsen.”   
\m
\v 10 “Necc ufiɣ Israil am uḍiř di řexřa, ẓriɣ řejdud nwem am yimenza n wartu di temẓi nsen. Nitni \add maca\add* udfen ɣar Baɛl-Faɣur uca wcin ixef nsen s řefḍiḥet \add i netta\add* uca nitni dewřen d nnɛawat am wenni tuɣa ttexsen. \x ◘ \xo 9:10 \xt Řxř. 25:3; Izhd. 106:28\x*  
\v 11 \add X yinni n\add* Ifrayim, aqa aɛuǧi nsen ad iḍu am wejḍiḍ, \add ad yaggʷej\add* x wexřaq u x uɛeddis \add n yemmas\add* u x tkessit n tarwa.  
\v 12 Waxxa nitni ssyamen iḥenjiren nsen ař ɣa mɣaren, Necc ad ten arreɣ nhřa iḥenjiren ařami war din iqqim bnadem. Maɣar uřa i nitni \add s tidett\add*, uct, xmi xasen ɣa ḥeyydeɣ.  
\v 13 Axmi ẓriɣ Ṣur, ammu i ittwaẓẓu Ifrayim deg ict n jjihet arḍan. U řexxu \add ittxeṣṣa i\add* Ifrayim ad isellem tarwa nnes i uqettař.  
\v 14 Ewc asen, \add a\add* SIDI! Min i ɣa tewced? Ewc asen ijj n uɛeddis s weṭṭuw n iseyman d yebbac yuẓɣen. \x ◘ \xo 9:14 \xt Lk. 23:29\x*  
\v 15 Marra taɛeffant nsen \add tɛarra\add* di Jiljal, maɣar dinni carheɣ ten x tɛeffant n tmegga nsen. Necc ad xasen aẓẓřeɣ zi Taddart inu. Ɛemmarṣ ɛad ad ten xseɣ \add ɛad\add*, marra řḥukkam nsen d imɣewwɣen. \x ◘ \xo 9:15 \xt Ica. 1:23; Ḥuc. 4:15; 12:12\x*  
\v 16 Ifrayim ittwawwet, iẓewran nsen uẓɣen, war ttirwen ɛad. Waxxa nitni ttarwen, Necc ad nɣeɣ imɛizzan n uɛeddis nsen.  
\v 17 AREBBI inu ad ten inḍar, maɣar nitni war ɣares ttesřin, u nitni ad dewřen ttᵉtliɛen jar řegnus.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\m
\v 1 “Israil d ict n tzayart tewseɛ, tenni i dd ittawyen řɣiǧet i yixef nnes. Mammec tuɣa řɣiǧet nnes temmarni, ammu i dd-mmarenyen uřa d iɛalṭaren nnes, mecḥař tecna temmurt nnes, ammu i ggin nitni uřa d imayḍuten \add iqeddsen\add* cnan. \x ◘ \xo 10:1 \xt Ḥuc. 8:11\x*  
\v 2 Uř nsen aqa ittwabḍa, řexxu aqa daysen řɛib. Netta ad yarẓ iɛalṭaren nsen, Netta ad ihdem imayḍuten nsen \add iqeddsen\add*  
\v 3 Maɣar řexxu qqaren: ‘Neccin war ɣarneɣ bu ujeǧid, maɣar neccin war neggʷid ca SIDI, u \add ɛad mařa tuɣa din\add* ajeǧid: ‘Min izemmar ad aneɣ igg?’ \x ◘ \xo 10:3 \xt Ḥuc. 3:4\x*  
\v 4 Ssawařen awařen \add ixwan\add*, ttjaǧan ẓur am tteggen ijj n řɛahd, uca řḥukm \add idweř\add* ittgeɛɛed am yijj n řeɛceb amesmum di řexḍuḍ n iyyaren.  
\v 5 Imezdaɣ n Samarya ad nnxeřɛen zi ssibbet n uɛejmi n Bayt-Awan, maɣar řgens nnes ad xas icḍen, uca uřa d ikehhanen nnes ad xas ceḍnen, x uɛuǧi nnes, maɣar wanita ittwakkes zzayes.  
\v 6 Ad t awyen ɣar Accur d tarzeft i ujeǧid Yarib. Ifrayim ad igg řefḍiḥet i uzeǧif nnes u Israil ad iseḍḥa zi lqarar nnes.  
\v 7 Ittwassesqar ujeǧid n Samarya am ukuffu x wudem n waman.  
\v 8 Ad ttwahedment řegɛudi n Awan, aqa-tent d ddenb n Israil. Isennanen d tzeggʷart ad uɛřan x iɛalṭaren nsen u nitni ad inin i idurar: ‘Dřem aneɣ!’ u i tewririn: ‘Wḍant-i-dd xaneɣ!’ \x ◘ \xo 10:8 \xt Ica. 2:19; Lk. 23:30; Asa. 6:16; 9:6\x*  
\v 9 Zeg wussan n Jibɛa teggid ddnub, \add a\add* Israil. Dinni qqimen nitni bedden, \add iwa,\add* war ten iřeqqif řatar n umenɣi ak-d ayt n řmuɛṣiyyet di Jibɛa. \x ◘ \xo 10:9 \xt Ḥuc. 9:9\x*  
\v 10 Aqa dayi meẓri ḥima ad ten carfeɣ u ad xasen ssmuneɣ řegnus xmi ten ɣa carfeɣ s tnayen n ixeṭṭan nsen.”   
\b  
\m
\v 11 “Ifrayim d ict n tɛejmit ittwadarrben, tᵉttexs ad tessarwet. Necc ɛduɣ x tcuni n yiri nnes. Necc ad nedheɣ Ifrayim, Yahuda ad icarz, Yaɛqub ad inqec \add temmurt\add* i yixef nnes. \f ◼ \fr 10:11 \ft \+fk Necc ɛduɣ x tcuni n yiri nnes\ft  - ixs ad yini belli ittwagg ijj n zzayru x yiri nnes.\f*  
\v 12 Zarɛem tasegda i yixef nwem, mjarem tamexsiwt icewwaren maḥend ad \add zzayes\add* tɛemmarem aqemmum nwem, carzem ijj n yeyyar ixwa i yixef nwem, minzi aqa-t d řḥař maḥend ad tarzum x SIDI, ař dd ɣa yas Netta u ad yarra tasegda ad xawem teccat am wenẓar.”\x ◘ \xo 10:12 \xt Irm. 4:3\x*   
\m
\v 13 “Aqa kenniw tcarzem min war iḥřin, tṣeyyfem řmuɛṣiyyet, teccim řɣiǧet n uxarriq, maɣar cek tᵉtecřed x webrid \add i tixḍared simant\add* nnec, x ubarru n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt nnec.  
\v 14 Ad ikkar ijj n ddriz n umenɣi ḍidd i řgens nnec u marra lqelɛat nnec ad ttwahedment am mammec ihdem Calman Bayt-Arbil deg wass n umenɣi, umi tᵉttwařbez ict n yemmas ak-d iḥenjiren \add nnes\add*.  
\v 15 Ammu i igga Bayt-Il akidwem zi ssibbet n tuɛeffna nwem yuǧɣen. Ɣar řefjar ad ittwaseɣḍ ujeǧid n Israil s ijj n useɣd qaɛ.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\m
\v 1 “Ařami tuɣa Israil \add ɛad\add* d aḥenjir, tuɣa ttexseɣ t u Necc řaɣiɣ-dd i mmi zi Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 11:1 \xt Uf. 4:22-23: Mt. 2:15\x*  
\v 2 \add Uřa d inabiyyen inu\add* řaɣan xasen, \add maca xenni\add* aggʷejen nitni \add deɣya\add* x iɣembab nsen maḥend ad awyen tiɣarṣa i ‘Ibaɛlen’ d tewhibin n řebxur i řexyařat nsen ineqcen.  
\v 3 D Necc i tuɣa isseřmaden ticři i Ifrayim, \add wah,\add* Netta iksi ten x iɣaǧen nnes, \add maca\add* nitni war ssinen ca aqa Necc d wenni i ten issgenfan.  
\v 4 S tesɣunin n bnadem jebdeɣ ten-dd \add ɣari\add*, s tmurar n tmexsiwt, u Necc tuɣa i nitni am wenni dd-issgeɛɛaden zzayřet zeg iɣesmiren nsen, u Necc sswiẓẓḍeɣ as \add ifassen inu\add* maḥend ad as wceɣ ad icc.”   
\b  
\m
\v 5 “Netta war dd-ittarri s uzeǧif ɣar Miṣra. Accur, netta \add ad yiři\add* d ajeǧid nnes, maɣar nitni ugin ad dd-dewřen.  
\v 6 Ssif ad inneḍ di tneddam nsen uca ad yareddeǧ iɛumad nnes \add n ubelleɛ n tewwura\add* u ad ten yecc zi ssibbet n ixarriṣen \add n yixef\add* nsen.  
\v 7 \add Maɣar\add* řgens inu iqqim ittneqřab xafi. Nitni ttřaɣan jmiɛ ɣar sennej, \add maca\add* Netta war ten issɛuǧi ca.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Arreḥmet n SIDI x Ifrayim  
\m
\v 8 “Mammec zemmareɣ Necc ad cek sellmeɣ, Ifrayim? \add Mammec zemmareɣ Necc\add* ad cek sellmeɣ, Israil? \add Mammec zemmareɣ Necc\add* ad cek sellmeɣ am Adama, ad cek ggeɣ \add d amedya\add* am Ṣabuyim? Uř inu inneḥweř zzayi, aziǧez inu ittextux jmiɛ. \x ◘ \xo 11:8 \xt Amz. 19:24; Aɛwd. 29:22\x*  
\v 9 Necc war tejjiɣ ad arxuɣ řḥaduq n weɣḍab inu, Necc war dd-ddikkwiřeɣ ca maḥend ad areddǧeɣ Ifrayim, maɣar Necc d Arebbi u Necc war ǧiɣ d bnadem, Necc d Amqeddas di řwesṭ nnec, war dd-ttiseɣ ca s tmessi \add n lɣaḍab inu\add*.  
\v 10 Nitni ad gguren awarni i SIDI. Netta ad issmuhrut am yijj n weyrad, maɣar ad issmuhrut Netta uca iḥenjiren ad dd-asen ttarjijin zi tma n řebḥar.  
\v 11 Am ijḍaḍ ad dd-asen ttarjijin zi temmurt n Miṣra u am tedbirt zi temmurt n Accur u Necc ad ten sszedeɣ di tudrin nsen, iqqar SIDI.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 12
\s1 Ifrayim d usřif nnes Yaɛqub  
\m
\v 1 “Ifrayim ittenneḍ ayi s uxarriq u taddart n Israil s řɣecc, \add maca\add* Yahuda ittetliɛ ɛad ak-d Arebbi u ak-d Umqeddas Ameqqran d amtiqqi.  
\v 2 Ifrayim d ijj n umeksaw yuyur awarni i usemmiḍ. Ass marra yarenni ixarriqen d ureddeǧ. Nitni ggin ijj n řɛahd ak-d Accur uca ttawyen zzect ɣar Miṣra.”   
\b  
\m
\v 3 “SIDI ɣares ijj n umcubbec ak-d Yahuda u Netta ad igg s Yaɛqub ɛlaḥsab ibriden nnes, ad t ixeǧeṣ am mammec timegga nnes.  
\v 4 Deg uɛeddis n yemmas iṭṭef umas ɣar unirz u řami tuɣa \add d aryaz\add* ijhed immɛařa ak-d AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 12:4 \xt Amz. 25:26; 35:9, 10 \x*  
\v 5 Netta tuɣa immneɣ ak-d lmalak uca iɣřeb. Iru, iḥeccem i-t. Yufa i-t di Bayt-Il u dinni issiweř Netta akidneɣ, \x ◘ \xo 12:5 \xt Amz. 28:12, 19; 35:7, 14, 15\x*  
\v 6 \add wah,\add* SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat, SIDI d Isem nnes i řidaret.  
\v 7 Dweř ɣar AREBBI nnec, ḥḍa tamexsiwt icewwaren d řḥeqq, u sitim řebda i AREBBI nnec.”   
\b  
\m
\v 8 “Kenɛan ɣares ijj n řmizan iɣecc deg ufus nnes, itteɛjib as ad ibeɛɛej.  
\v 9 \add Maca\add* Ifrayim iqqar: ‘Necc dewřeɣ d bu-wagřa, yarweɣ ict n řeksibet d tameqqrant i yixef inu. \add Di\add* marra řxedmet inu war dayi ttifen ca řmuɛṣiyyet nni \add iǧan\add* d ddenb.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 10 “Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nnec, zeg \add wami teffɣem kenniw zi\add* temmurt n Miṣra. Necc ad cek jjeɣ ad tzedɣed deg iqiḍan am deg wussan n tmesmunt \add di řexřa\add*. \x ◘ \xo 12:10 \xt Ica. 43:11\x*  
\v 11 Necc ad ssiwřeɣ ɣar inabiyyen u Necc ad arniɣ řewḥiy aṭṭas u s ufus n inabiyyen ad ssiwřeɣ s řemtuř.”   
\b  
\m
\v 12 “Mařa \add tuɣa\add* Jilɛad d řmuɛṣiyyet, \add xenni\add* dewřen nitni xwan qaɛ di Jilɛad. Aqa qeddmen \add din\add* ifunasen. Uřa d iɛalṭaren nsen dewřen d iɛurricen n iẓra di řexḍuḍ n iyyaren.\x ◘ \xo 12:12 \xt Ḥuc. 4:15; 6:8; 9:15\x*  
\v 13 Yaɛqub yarweř ɣar jjwayeh n Aram u Israil tuɣa ittsexxar x yict n temɣart, u netta yarwes \add taḥimart\add* di ṭṭweɛ n yict n temɣart, \x ◘ \xo 12:13 \xt Amz. 28:5; 29:20, 28\x*  
\v 14 \add maca\add* s yijj n unabi issgeɛɛed SIDI Israil zi Miṣra u s yijj n unabi yarwes i-t.  
\v 15 Ifrayim tuɣa isɛar i-t aṭṭas. S uya ad yejj \add SIDI\add* idammen nnes ad xas dd-asen u Sidi nnes ad as ixeǧeṣ řḥegra nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 12:15 \xt Ica. 65:7\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 13
\s1 SIDI d Arebbi n Ifrayim  
\m
\v 1 “Umi issiweř Ifrayim, \add aqa din\add* tarjijet \add s uweqqar\add*. Netta issgeɛɛed ixef nnes di Israil uca idweř d amednub zi ssibbet \add n weɛbed nnes i\add* Baɛl, uca \add xenni\add* immut.  
\v 2 Uca řexxu \add ɛawed\add* arnin tteggen ddnub u ggin s nnuqart nsen ijj n řexyař ifesyen ɛlaḥsab řeɛqeř nsen, aqa-tent d řexyařat n l’aṣnam marra, řxedmet n umziř. Nitni qqaren xasen: ‘Ejj iwdan inni i ɣa iwehhben tiɣarṣa ad ssudumen iɛejmiyyen-a!’ \x ◘ \xo 13:2 \xt Ḥuc. 8:6\x*  
\v 3 S uya ad dewřen am yijj n useynu n ṣṣbeḥ u am nnda ɣar tuffut nni deɣya iɛeddun, am uřum iṭṭawen zeg unedrar u am ddexxan \add itteffɣen\add* zi tburjet.”   
\b  
\m
\v 4 “Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nnec, zeg \add wami dd-teffɣem kenniw zi\add* temmurt n Miṣra. Cek war tᵉttessned bu arebbi nneɣni mɣir Necc u war din Amsenjem mɣir Necc. \x ◘ \xo 13:4 \xt 2 Ṣm. 22:32; Izhd. 18:32; Ica. 43:11; Ḥuc. 12:10\x*  
\v 5 Necc ssneɣ cek di řexřa, deg ict n temmurt n řeḥmu yareqqen.  
\v 6 Ařami \add iwḍen\add* ɣar ddemnet nsen n tarewsa, dewřen jjiwnen. Ařami jjiwnen, innurfeɛ wuř nsen. X uya ttun ayi. \x ◘ \xo 13:6 \xt Aɛwd. 32:15; Ḥuc. 8:14\x*  
\v 7 S uyenni Necc dewřeɣ i nitni am weyrad izehharen, am uɣiřas řebteɣ deg webrid.  
\v 8 Necc usiɣ-dd ɣarsen am yijj n ddub wenni umi ucaren tarwa nnes u Necc ařẓeɣ idmaren nsen u ṣarḍeɣ ten din am tizemt. Řewḥuc n řexřa mezzqen ten.” \f ◼ \fr 13:8 \ft \+fk idmaren nsen\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ařeḥḥef n wuř nsen’.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 “Man aya idweř d akeḥḥeḍ nnec, \add a\add* Israil, aqa \add tɛekksed\add* ayi, ḍidd i Wenni iǧan d amɛawen nnec.  
\v 10 Mani \add iǧa xenni\add* ujeǧid nnec, d wenni izemmaren ad cek issenjem di marra tineddam nnec! U \add mani ǧan\add* řquḍat nnec umi tennid: ‘Ewc ayi ijj n ujeǧid uřa d řḥukkam’?  
\v 11 S weɣḍab inu wciɣ ac ijj n ujeǧid u s uduqqez inu \add n ufugem\add* kkseɣ ac t. \x ◘ \xo 13:11 \xt 1 Ṣm. 8:5; 15:23; 16:1\x*  
\v 12 Řmuɛṣiyyet n Ifrayim tᵉttwaqebbeḍ \add am deg ict n tqebbiḍṭ\add*, ddnub nnes ttwaḥḍan.  
\v 13 Řeḥriq n tarwa ad ɣares dd-yas. Netta d ijj n uḥenjir \add iqqim\add* břa tiɣit, maɣar netta war din ibedd di řweqt nnes \add maḥend ad iffeɣ\add*  
\m xmi i ɣa tarzem \add řemřawřet\add* ḥima \add ad ffɣen\add* iḥenjiren.   
\b  
\m
\v 14 “Zeg ufus n řaxart ad ten fdiɣ, ad ten fekkeɣ zi řmewt. \add A\add* řmewt, mani ǧan \add řeḥřacat n\add* ṭṭaɛun nnem, \add a\add* řaxart, mani \add teǧa\add* turṣuḍi nnem? \add Ma\add* ad nedmeɣ \add ɛad\add*? \add Lla,\add* aya inuffar zzat i tiṭṭawin inu. \x ◘ \xo 13:14 \xt Ica. 25:8; 1 Kur. 15:55\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 15 Waxxa ggur Ifrayim ad iwc řɣiǧet jar aytmas, \add ɛad\add* ad dd-yas ijj n usemmiḍ zi ccarq, ijj n usemmiḍ n SIDI nni i-dd i ɣa ikkaren, - tařa nnes ggur ad taẓeɣ, anu nnes ggur ad iwḍa - ggur ad ikecceḍ usemmiḍ ict n txabect zi mkuř řeqcuɛ iɣřan.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 14
\s1 Tařaɣit i ttubet  
\m
\v 1 “Samarya ad tᵉṭṭef axeǧeṣ, minzi tɣewweɣ x AREBBI nnes. Ad wḍan s ssif. Iḥenjiren imeẓyanen nsen ad ttwařebzen u timɣarin nsen s ddeyset ad ttwacarrgent. \x ◘ \xo 14:1 \xt Ḥuc. 10:14\x*  
\v 2 \add A\add* Israil, dweř-dd ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, maɣar tenderfed s řmuɛṣiyyet nnec. \x ◘ \xo 14:2 \xt Ḥuc. 12:7\x*  
\v 3 Ksim awařen\add -a\add* \add n ttubet\add* akidwem u dewřem-dd ɣar SIDI. Inim as: Ksi \add xaneɣ\add* řmuɛṣiyyet marra u qbeř \add zzayneɣ\add* min icnan, \add xenni\add* ad nawi \add s tidett\add* ifunasen d taḍḥiyet \add ɛlaḥsab řwuɛud\add* n iyencicen nneɣ.  
\v 4 Accur war d aneɣ issenjam, war neggur x yeysan u war neqqar i tmegga n ifassen nneɣ: ‘Arebbi nneɣ’, maɣar zzayek i ɣa ittwarḥem uyujiř.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 5 “Necc ad ten ssgenfiɣ zi tɣennant nsen, ad ten ttexseɣ s řxaḍar, maɣar aɣḍab inu iḥeyyed xas.  
\v 6 Necc ad iřiɣ i Israil am nnda. Netta ad inuwwar am tnewwact n tellilict, ad iwwet \add Israil\add* iẓewran nnes am \add idurar n\add* Lubnan. \f ◼ \fr 14:6 \ft \+fk tillilicin\ft  - ijj n marka n nnuwarat i daysen aẓri aṭṭas.\f*  
\v 7 Řefruɛ nnes ad zzuggarten u aweqqar nnes ad yiři am uzemmur u řefwaḥ nnes am \add řefwaḥ n tcejjura x idurar\add* n Lubnan.  
\v 8 Nitni ad dd-dewřen, ad qqimen di tiři nnes, ad sseddaren imendi, ad newwaren am tzayart. Řidaret nnes ad tiři axmi binu n Lubnan.  
\v 9 \add A\add* Ifrayim ad yini: ‘Min ɣari ɛad ak-d řexyařat n l’aṣnam?’ Necc sřiɣ \add as\add* u ad xas ssijjeɣ. Ad iřiɣ am yict n tcejjart n umerzi aziza, zzayi i tᵉttwaf řɣiǧet nnec.”\f ◼ \fr 14:9 \ft \+fk amerzi\ft  - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 “Man wen iǧan d amiɣis d afehham di tmesřayin-a, man wen i ɣar teǧa řefhamet u man wen i tent issnen? Wah, ibriden n SIDI nican i yeǧan u imseggaden ad daysen uyuren, maca inni iɛeddan ad daysen nnderfen.”   